•Popular : The app should have more than 10,000 down- loads on Google Play ( https://play.google.com/ ).

To facilitate the compilation and reproduction tasks, we considered only faulty apps developed in Android Studio (https://developer.android.com/studio/ ).
•Change the version of the Gradle ( https://gradle.org ) plugin in the dependencies (in most cases with version 2.3.3).
